title: Hurricane Ike Distruction in My Neighborhood Pictures
description:
This is some of the distruction that I had with Hurrican Ike in my Neighborhood.   Power came back on last night thankfully but most of Houston is still out of power still....


it will be a while before Houston and other areas get back to normal but every one is pulling together looking better as the days go on.....


And to the convoy to power crews for all over    Thank you so much!!!!!



Crane Dude
